{
  "stem": "27335.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were able to bust out, to-- to shred the German mobile radio station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And I gave him exact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had artillery-- my God, they blasted it to slivers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I never met any of these people, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I-- I just took a-- took up some job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was two Polish Jews here who were in contact with a Hungarian plumber, and they were builders, you see.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're doing these alterations you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And John told me, the Hungarian plumber-- I lived in his house-- these people, they wanted and they want to help.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] you want to work?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh yes, because I had-- I had nothing, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then came the tobacco harvest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I went to the Hungarian farmers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then and there I did [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, I went out in the second-- no, the last-- [INAUDIBLE] in August, when they started it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was coming to the end of September-- to September, when the manager of our paper, just on a Sunday afternoon, just walked into the farm where I was so-- I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And pack up and go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hold it now-- I have a couple more days-- a couple more days, and I don't want to leave this because we were good workers, and they were good-- good bosses and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Made good food and so on, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I want to finish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't want to leave them at the last moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I get disability pension, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this area, this 200-acre farm, you see it from here, that [INAUDIBLE] dairy, that was the farm there, the [INAUDIBLE] farm, the name of it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a road in from-- from-- highway-- highway 7.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
